# Test Plan  
Application: TutorialNinja Demo  
Prepared By: Senior QA Engineer  
Version: 1.0

## 1. Objective
Validate functionality, performance, usability, and reliability of the e-commerce application.

## 2. Scope
Includes UI functionality, login, registration, cart, checkout, and product flows.

## 3. Inclusions
- User account flows
- Product catalog flows
- Cart behavior
- Checkout process
- Negative scenarios

## 4. Exclusions
- Backend database checks
- Load testing
- API testing

## 5. Test Environment
- URL: http://www.tutorialsninja.com/demo/
- Browsers: Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari
- OS: Windows, macOS

## 6. Test Strategy
### 6.1 Testing Types
- Functional Testing  
- Regression Testing  
- Smoke Testing  
- UI Testing  
- Cross Browser  

### 6.2 Approach
- Create detailed test cases
- Execute priority-based testing
- Log defects in Jira/Excel

## 7. Test Schedule
| Activity | Duration |
|----------|----------|
| Test Planning | 1 day |
| Test Case Design | 4 days |
| Execution | 7 days |
| Regression | 3 days |

## 8. Deliverables
- Test Cases
- RTM
- Execution Report
- Defect Report
- Test Summary Report

## 9. Entry Criteria
- Requirements finalized
- Test environment ready

## 10. Exit Criteria
- All critical test cases executed
- No severity 1 defects open

## 11. Tools
- Jira / Excel  
- Selenium / Playwright  

## 12. Risks & Mitigation
| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| UI changes | Use stable locators |
| Environment down | Plan buffer time |

## 13. Approvals
QA Lead  
Product Owner  
